replies.msg:
Steven Gerrard: &ldquo;I think Jurgen Klopp is the best manager in the world. He just works for Liverpool. He has come and taken the club to the next level. When Jurgen delivers the league they should already be starting work on a statue of him.&rdquo; 🔴<br />
<br />
Gerrard: &ldquo;Looking in from the outside now, Liverpool is a machine both on and off the pitch. I envy those players. I wish I was 30 rather than 40 because I&rsquo;d love to be involved in that. I love the club. It has got a special place in my heart and it always will have.&rdquo;

